{"tid":1932934,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警方去信中西區區議會 批評議員以「黑警」侮辱警員及打斷發言 行為卑劣","createTime":"2020-03-19T04:07:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-19T04:20:38.000Z","uid":21470,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"7c869bad5599278ce7a91a7af9155bff32ae09a4","tid":1932934,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T04:07:03.000Z","msg":"警方去信中西區區議會 批評葉錦龍和甘乃威針對警隊<br />\n<br />\n警方去信中西區區議會主席鄭麗琼，點名批評交通及運輸委員會主席葉錦龍和民主黨區議員甘乃威，在會議上針對和侮辱警方，無助警方和區議會合作，要求鄭麗琼正視和譴責。<br />\n<br />\n警方在信中表示，葉錦龍在上周四的會議，要求出席會議的警方代表出示委任證核實身份，但核實身份的工作，理應是中西區民政事務處負責，葉錦龍依然作出毫無根據的指控，不讓警方回應，更無理要求秘書處刪除警方發言紀錄，並將警方因為不滿遭不公平對待而離開會議室，扭曲為被趕離場，警方批評葉錦龍矮化警隊，對會議主持手法表示強烈不滿和極度遺憾。警方又批評甘乃威多次口出惡言，以「黑警」侮辱警員，又打斷警方發言，行為卑劣。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1274928&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1274928%26csid%3D261_341&d=AthmRk%2BBSDjaWf6zT95BzNTLU9NF7cMiG%2FeCYohcYb8%3D&h=6e116305\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1274928&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"bb5d858c6d48db8248a5bcb947325e98f483d421","tid":1932934,"uid":192824,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T04:07:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>黑警<br />\n<br />\n殺警</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"331c5ce4a9c6662ea47032f0c21c129c5c477e61","tid":1932934,"uid":126621,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T04:08:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/WT3k7gzeikE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FWT3k7gzeikE&d=AthmRk%2BBSDjaWf6zT95BzNTLU9NF7cMiG%2FeCYohcYb8%3D&h=93453e70\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/WT3k7gzeikE</a>"},{"pid":"c98a952141dbc5b3e9c46bfb1c896fbc1843bfd5","tid":1932934,"uid":225130,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T04:08:41.000Z","msg":"惡過希特拉"},{"pid":"195b93b3b5a3a9a055aced3aadc5f0b988450ecf","tid":1932934,"uid":144626,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T04:09:19.000Z","msg":"你地叫示威者甲由仲卑劣"},{"pid":"bf99697a81ceef542dca63818271d5b386ae233f","tid":1932934,"uid":2772,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T04:09:35.000Z","msg":"啱呀<br />\n我都覺得叫黑警都已經多餘<br />\n叫返「警察」都已經夠低賤<br />\n唔洗幫你分黑唔黑<br />\n<br />\n正如我唔會叫中國人做中國賤人一樣"},{"pid":"136c52e8b7e0e6220098a2a78fd6fbc7fbe85326","tid":1932934,"uid":119188,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T04:10:37.000Z","msg":"佢叫示威者暴徒又點計"},{"pid":"5d27209ed23c53dd187dda5656e3ff0d87ad0271","tid":1932934,"uid":3457,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T04:10:38.000Z","msg":"你地叫曱甴阻止人地講自己個名就好正義？"},{"pid":"c7beebd48b4ffb75f4dea9d7aaa2e945e8618d2e","tid":1932934,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T04:10:38.000Z","msg":"公開撕爛封信啦"},{"pid":"864fba5638b42910fd9c76fe36f376dd07f481c3","tid":1932934,"uid":41290,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T04:11:10.000Z","msg":"班警甴有資格用卑劣呢個字咩"},{"pid":"da61a069fc82c5cc213ee9426bdcf39027316309","tid":1932934,"uid":108757,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T04:12:11.000Z","msg":"又唔係叫你，你係黑警咩？"},{"pid":"48840f0b214207d0f43c6111d99f49336d7fad9a","tid":1932934,"uid":4964,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T04:15:03.000Z","msg":"不評論個別事件，但區議會一直以不偏不倚嘅態度處理"},{"pid":"9eba471d697ab6c88324ec919c3f18d4b1c39137","tid":1932934,"uid":39872,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T04:20:38.000Z","msg":"我日日都對住警察局講黑警死全家，你又奈得我咩何"}]}